WEBVTT

00:03:29.702 --> 00:03:31.322
that rubber-band trick.

00:03:31.346 --> 00:03:33.969
You moms remember what I'm talking about?

00:03:33.993 --> 00:03:35.852
The rubber band through the buttonhole,

00:03:35.876 --> 00:03:37.433
around the button and back?

00:03:37.457 --> 00:03:38.734
Instant stretch.

00:03:39.358 --> 00:03:40.884
So I removed the zipper

00:03:41.837 --> 00:03:44.201
so he could pull it
up and down on his own.

00:03:44.225 --> 00:03:48.073
I cut up the side seam
of the bottom of his pants

00:03:48.097 --> 00:03:50.118
to accommodate for his leg braces,

00:03:50.142 --> 00:03:51.663
applied Velcro --

00:03:51.687 --> 00:03:55.308
hold your ears, everybody:
peel and stick, mind you --

00:03:55.332 --> 00:03:57.248
so that it would close around it.

00:03:58.237 --> 00:04:02.077
When I showed Oliver
my arts and crafts project,